title: 290 - The Blackout
description:
Are you operating in the gift God has given you? In this episode, the guys encourage you to use & operate in the gift God has blessed you with to live your life to the fullest. If you don't use it you will lose it! Also, recognize that your gift will make enough room for you. Make sure you use it to the fullest, and if you don't know your gift yet, keep pushing until you find it.
